headline.main: Bednik, Larin Help Orlando City Beat NYCFC 1-0 in Opener
headline.print_headline: Bednik, Larin Help Orlando City Beat NYCFC 1-0 in Opener

lead_paragraph: Cyle Larin scored the first goal at the new Orlando City Stadium, Joe Bendik had seven saves and Orlando City beat New York City FC 1-0 on Sunday night in the season opener for both teams.
